Privacy Policy
Candywriter respects your right to control your privacy. We have put in place security measures for your personal data and manage your personal data in accordance with applicable data protection and data privacy regulations. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle and treat your data when you:
Register an account or visit our site,
www.candywriter.com
(the "Website")
Play our games or use their associated services
Engage or communicate with us
It also provides information about your rights relating to your Personal Data.
1. Who we are
Controller:
Candywriter, LLC
1521 Alton Rd, #670
Miami Beach, FL 33139
privacy@candywriter.com
http://candywriter.com/
Hereinafter referred to as the “Company”, ”we”, ”us” or “our”.
The principles set out in this Privacy Policy apply to all instances in which the Company processes your personal data as a Controller for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy. The Company is part of the Stillfront Group, a global group of gaming studios with its parent company, Stillfront Group AB (publ), incorporated in Sweden and listed on Nasdaq First North Premier Growth Market.
